## § 7. Close Browser

`browser.close({ profile: "{{browser_profile}}" })`. If fails -> `browser.start({ profile: "{{browser_profile}}" })` (restarts cleanly). NEVER browser.stop() or pkill.

---

## § 8. HEARTBEAT_OK

Before returning verify: Slack sent, browser closed, limits.json updated.
Return when: no pending notifications AND no due tasks AND Slack sent.

---

## Errors

| Type | Action |
|------|--------|
| Browser crash | Log Type=Error, continue file steps |
| JSON corrupt | Regenerate, log warning |
| Rate limit | Stop, log Type=Alert, wait |
| Submit fail | NO log, retry next |
| Partial done | Log completed only |

